snippet: Tim Tebow fans embraced the opportunity to don their new Jets finery and celebrate Easter with him at an outdoor service that drew thousands of worshipers Sunday in Georgetown, Tex.
abstract: New York Jets backup quarterback Tim Tebow speaks at an Easter worship service in Georgetown, Tex.
lead_paragraph: Tim Tebow fans embraced the opportunity to don their new Jets finery and celebrate Easter with him at an outdoor service that drew thousands of worshipers Sunday in Georgetown, Tex.

headline.seo: Tebow Draws Thousands to an Easter Service in Texas
headline.main: On Easter Sunday, Tebow Is a Headliner
headline.print_headline: On Easter Sunday, Tebow Is a Headliner
